    {
      "text": "Bike Daisuki! Hashiriya Kon - Rider's Spirits (バイク大好き！走り屋魂; lit. \"I Love Bikes! Race Ya Soul\") is a 1994 video game for the Super Famicom. It is a racing game that allows players to race on motorcycles.",
